                  ></path><path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="M512 64C264.6 64 64 264.6 64 512s200.6 448 448 448s448-200.6 448-448S759.4 64 512 64m0 820c-205.4 0-372-166.6-372-372s166.6-372 372-372s372 166.6 372 372s-166.6 372-372 372"
                  ></path></svg
                ></span
              >Serve a warm meal
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-start items-center gap-2 text-xl">
              <span
                ><svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="1024"
                  height="1024"
                  viewBox="0 0 1024 1024"
                  class="h-6 w-6"
                  ><title>Check-circle-outlined SVG Icon</title><path
