            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-start items-center gap-2 text-xl">
              <span
                ><svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="1024"
                  height="1024"
                  viewBox="0 0 1024 1024"
                  class="h-6 w-6"
                  ><title>Check-circle-outlined SVG Icon</title><path
